00:17:29.330 --> 00:17:31.080
Throw, D'Arby.

00:17:31.510 --> 00:17:34.390
Will you believe me or not?

00:17:40.070 --> 00:17:42.470
Here it comes! It's coming
straight down the middle!

00:17:42.470 --> 00:17:43.820
It's a straight!

00:17:43.820 --> 00:17:46.340
But is it going to remain a straight?!

00:17:46.820 --> 00:17:49.090
Will it fall or not?

00:17:50.230 --> 00:17:53.600
He swung! Jotaro bet on the forkball!

00:17:53.830 --> 00:17:57.060
But it's not falling! It's staying straight!

00:17:58.230 --> 00:18:00.520
He caught the bottom of the ball!

00:18:02.520 --> 00:18:03.480
Out!

00:18:03.840 --> 00:18:06.530
Top of the first, three outs! Change!

00:18:06.530 --> 00:18:09.530
Top of the 1st

00:18:10.540 --> 00:18:12.400
How could you be so stupid?!

00:18:12.400 --> 00:18:14.890
You actually believed him

00:18:14.890 --> 00:18:17.460
and swung for a forkball!

00:18:18.930 --> 00:18:19.890
No.

00:18:20.370 --> 00:18:24.180
He was certain that I would swing for a forkball,

00:18:24.740 --> 00:18:26.600
so he changed it to a straight fastball.

00:18:27.160 --> 00:18:31.720
As he said, ever since we entered
this mansion, I've been uncertain.

00:18:32.240 --> 00:18:37.390
He somehow knew that Star Platinum
would throw a right punch.

00:18:37.890 --> 00:18:42.200
I-Impossible! So are you telling me

00:18:42.570 --> 00:18:45.750
that he's reading your mind?

00:18:46.130 --> 00:18:49.450
Next is the bottom of the first.
It's my turn on offense.

00:18:59.250 --> 00:19:01.540
This is a declaration that I will hit a home run.

00:19:01.870 --> 00:19:05.700
I shall hit the ball you throw into the left stands.

00:19:07.980 --> 00:19:10.510
Old man. You're certain that the game

00:19:10.510 --> 00:19:12.480
and console aren't rigged in any way, right?

00:19:12.480 --> 00:19:14.440
There's no chance of that.

00:19:14.440 --> 00:19:18.180
And I've been keeping my eye
out for any kind of cheating.

00:19:18.590 --> 00:19:21.270
That means the secret lies with his Stand.

00:19:21.270 --> 00:19:22.940
It doesn't just take souls.

00:19:23.330 --> 00:19:25.480
It has some kind of secret power.

00:19:27.760 --> 00:19:29.490
The course of action I'll take is...

00:19:33.040 --> 00:19:35.300
This should tell me something.

00:19:35.710 --> 00:19:39.750
What?! He's going to try to
hit the batter on purpose?

00:19:40.150 --> 00:19:43.880
Where might you be aiming to throw? Inside?

00:19:44.320 --> 00:19:45.690
Will it be high?

00:19:46.160 --> 00:19:47.370
Or low?

00:19:47.830 --> 00:19:50.750
Are you planning some sort of trick?

00:20:00.110 --> 00:20:03.690
What?! He dodged at the same
time as the pitch was thrown!

00:20:05.880 --> 00:20:07.230
Bazoom

00:20:07.340 --> 00:20:11.900
H-He read that! He perfectly read it!

00:20:12.290 --> 00:20:17.490
There's no way he could have done
that without reading Jotaro's mind.

00:20:17.490 --> 00:20:18.790
Home run!

00:20:21.920 --> 00:20:23.290
That's one run.

00:20:23.610 --> 00:20:25.230
I-Impossible.

00:20:25.670 --> 00:20:28.110
We've met all kinds up until now,

00:20:28.110 --> 00:20:30.650
but we've never seen a
Stand that could read minds.

00:20:30.650 --> 00:20:34.240
If it can read minds, then will no
amount of intelligence or power

00:20:34.240 --> 00:20:36.730
s-stand any chance against it?

00:20:37.200 --> 00:20:39.810
Wh-What are you going to do, Jotaro?!

00:20:49.250 --> 00:20:52.320
Bottom of the 1st

00:20:50.590 --> 00:20:52.320
Bam

00:20:52.500 --> 00:20:56.070
Damn it! H-He's declaring another home run.

00:20:56.570 --> 00:20:59.330
Will the next one be outside?

00:21:00.740 --> 00:21:02.660
And low?

00:21:02.660 --> 00:21:04.900
Or will it be a straight?

00:21:14.650 --> 00:21:16.220
Clang

00:21:16.680 --> 00:21:18.040
Home run!

00:21:18.580 --> 00:21:20.100
Four to two.

00:21:24.050 --> 00:21:27.190
By analyzing various data
and the situation you're in,

00:21:27.190 --> 00:21:29.580
you can figure out how an
opponent's mind works, to an extent.

00:21:29.580 --> 00:21:35.990
But this Stand can anticipate the
ball's course with perfect precision.

00:21:35.990 --> 00:21:37.530
And he's not cheating!

00:21:39.680 --> 00:21:42.470
Another home run! It's four to three!

00:21:42.870 --> 00:21:46.210
How can we stop him from reading our minds?

00:21:46.210 --> 00:21:47.550
How?

00:21:50.410 --> 00:21:52.940
I'm going to turn this around soon.

00:21:52.940 --> 00:21:55.260
Now, will the next one be inside?

00:21:55.260 --> 00:21:58.470
Down the middle? High? A changeup?

00:21:58.470 --> 00:21:59.810
I wonder where it'll go.

00:22:04.440 --> 00:22:05.810
Your hat...

00:22:05.810 --> 00:22:07.510
Heh, you fool.

00:22:07.510 --> 00:22:11.320
Do you think I'm using underhanded
methods, like my brother?

00:22:11.560 --> 00:22:13.260
Jotaro, that's not it!

00:22:13.260 --> 00:22:15.070
Hiding behind your hat won't help.

00:22:15.470 --> 00:22:19.320
He's not reading the reflection
of the screen in your eyes.

00:22:19.640 --> 00:22:22.730
And it's not a trick where
he's listening to your fingers

00:22:22.730 --> 00:22:25.580
as they push the buttons to figure
out what you're going to do.

00:22:26.010 --> 00:22:30.480
I've been watching him.
That's not what's going on.

00:22:30.480 --> 00:22:33.030
This is the first time I've
sweat or bled in a while.

00:22:33.030 --> 00:22:34.120
That's why I took it off.

00:22:34.660 --> 00:22:37.380
I'd like you to hurry up
and throw your next pitch.

00:22:38.710 --> 00:22:41.820
But I don't think I have to
worry about sweating anymore.

00:22:41.820 --> 00:22:43.390
I'm going to declare my pitch.

00:22:44.630 --> 00:22:47.140
It's going to be a straight,
high to the outside.

00:22:47.460 --> 00:22:48.850
What?

00:22:48.850 --> 00:22:51.900
Wh-What? What did you just say, Jotaro?!

00:22:51.900 --> 00:22:53.520
You heard me.

00:22:52.130 --> 00:23:08.110
Menacing

00:22:53.790 --> 00:22:56.420
Are you so old that your
hearing's gone, old man?

00:22:56.420 --> 00:22:58.860
I said I was going to declare my pitch.

00:22:59.190 --> 00:23:01.910
I'll throw a straight, high to the outside.

00:23:06.590 --> 00:23:08.120
Jotaro!

00:23:10.580 --> 00:23:22.340
Menacing

00:23:11.670 --> 00:23:15.330
Will you believe me or not?

00:23:18.090 --> 00:23:19.570
Are you stupid?

00:23:25.010 --> 00:23:26.930
Next Episode Preview

00:23:25.910 --> 00:23:27.890
What did you just say, Jotaro?!

00:23:27.890 --> 00:23:29.940
I said I was going to declare my pitch.

00:23:29.940 --> 00:23:31.920
Jotaro is not lying.

00:23:31.920 --> 00:23:32.410
Yes.

00:23:32.410 --> 00:23:33.930
You rigged the console somehow!

00:23:33.930 --> 00:23:34.440
No.

00:23:34.440 --> 00:23:36.820
Your school hat proves that you're cheating!

00:23:36.820 --> 00:23:39.990
It's not cheating if you don't get caught.

